data.eml:eml: Two new genera and two new species of cicadas from Central America (Hemiptera: Cicadidae: Cicadinae)

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Sanborn, Allen F. (2018): Two new genera and two new species of cicadas from Central America (Hemiptera: Cicadidae: Cicadinae). Zootaxa 4418 (2): 149-160, DOI: https://doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.4418.2.4
